sub_title: Happy outgoing English Teacher looking for a job in the Netherlands
summary:
My name is Yupa Tuytaisong and I was an English Teacher in Thailand for more than 8 years.
This involved making lesson plans, holding activities and giving presentations in PowerPoint. The ages of my students ranged from kindergarten to  junior high school students. 
I have a positive and friendly character and I like to help people. 
Talking to people comes naturally to me and people also enjoy talking to me.
One of my other abilities, is that I am very good with children. I can easily connect with them. 
I would like to find a job, where I can work with children or people.
